Dialogs.Dialog: I'm still mad at you. You should be sorry.
Today is Rinko's birthday. Do you want to celebrate？
Today is Rinko's birthday！ Of course you remember, right？
You didn't remember Rinko's birthday anyway.
You didn't show up for Rinko's birthday. I missed you.
Happy Birthday. Today is special, okay？ ...ejem... I love you▼
Happy Birthday！ You're getting old again, aren't you？ ...Joking！ Love.you▼
Nyanyanyanya！ ...ejem... It's happy birthday in cat language...
You're late. I've been waiting for you... Happy Birthday. Idiot.
Where have you been！ I couldn't tell you Happy Birthday... Idiot.
Happy Birthday！ I know I'm late, but Rinko won't forget you.
Do you remember it？ Today is the day when you and Rinko met for the first time. I don't think Rinko will ever forget that day.
Today is the day we first met, right？ ...You didn't forget, did you？
What day is it today？ Hehe... it's the day you and Rinko met for the first time, right？ Don't forget that, okay？
Today is the day we started dating, remember？ Thank you for loving Rinko.
Today is the day... Rinko confessed to you！ ...Yup. The sunset was beautiful, wasn't it？
What day is it today？ ...Hehe, yes, it's the day Rinko confessed her feelings.
Today... is the anniversary of the first time you and Rinko kissed. Did you remember？
Today is the anniversary of our first kiss. You remember, right？
Today is the anniversary of our first kiss... It's a little embarrassing.
Monday, huh. Another long week starts today...
Today is Tuesday, huh. Oh, I have to buy the magazine I always read.
It's Wednesday, the middle of the week. It's a bit dull.
On Thursday, I have a drama I want to watch.
It's Friday. I made it through another week.
Finally, it's Saturday. Thanks for your hard work all week.
Saturdays are the days I tend to stay up late.
It's a fun Sunday. What do you want to do today？
It's Sunday, but I think I like to laze around all day.
You meet more people when your environment changes, or so they say... It's nothing, forget it.
Ugh. Rinko doesn't like hot weather.
It's the holiday season. Hey, which do you like better, the sea or the mountains？
I guess Rinko's autumn is "autumn of reading".
Food is so good these days. Rinko doesn't mind autumn.
I like winter. I can go snowboarding and stuff.
In winter, I might like to take a nap at a kotatsu.
Happy New Year. I'm glad to be with you this year as well.
Did you have your first dream？ For Rinko... it's a secret.
What was your first dream like？ You... I won't tell it！
I had my first dream of us, together. I'm sure we'll be together all this year.
Ah, winter vacation is over. I feel so tired.
Did you try the rice gruel with the seven herbs？ Rinko ate it.
Coming of age day, huh. I hope we can stay together until we come of age.
I heard that today is Kagami Biraki. Did you know that？
Today, the oni is out, the good fortune is inside.
It's Risshun. It's called spring, but it's still cold...
National Day. It used to be called "Kiyoin-setsu" in the old days. I read it in a book.
Even Rinko remembers it. Valentine's Day...
Don't buy yourself any chocolate today！ I won't tell you why...
Are you expecting me by any chance？ Because today I'm going to... hehe.
Ah, this year is a leap year！ That's a special day once every four years.
It's almost time for the plum blossoms to bloom.
White Day, huh. Oh, I don't expect an expensive return gift.
...I don't have any expectations for White Day.
White Day, huh. Actually, I'm a little bit excited about it...
Today's the Vernal Equinox. It's the day when day and night are the same length.
It's almost spring break. Wanna go somewhere and have fun？
Yay. It's spring break. I can play games all day.
Today is the end... joking, it's April Fool's Day！
I hate you！ ...Hehe！ It's April Fool's Day！
Rinko is going on a trip today. A small lie▼ Are you surprised？
I guess today is the end of spring break. It's a hassle to go to school...
Cherry blossoms are in bloom. Do you like cherry blossom viewing？
Today is Showa Day. It used to be Emperor Showa's birthday.
It's almost the holidays. Wanna go somewhere？
Today is Constitution Day. It's when the Constitution of Japan went into effect.
Today is Greenery Day. It's a day to get close to nature.
Today is Children's Day. I'll make a carp streamer for my little brother.
Today is the first day of summer. According to the calendar, it is already summer.
Mother's Day. What should Rinko do？
I'm not good at sports festivals. I hate running.
Today is the summer solstice. It is the day with the longest daytime.
I'm changing into summer clothes today.
I'm thinking of buying a Father's Day present for my dad.
I heard that the beach will open soon. It's already summer.
It's the day when Orihime and Hikoboshi can meet... I hope it'll be fine.
Almost summer vacation. Can you take me somewhere？
Today is the day of the sea. Well, the fact that it is a national holiday means something.
Finally, summer vacation！ Now if only I didn't have homework...
According to the calendar, today's autumn. In reality, though, it's the height of summer.
Fireworks festivals are going on all over the place. Shall we go see them in yukata？
Today is Obon. Bon dance？ I don't dance.
Ah, summer vacation is over. I don't want to go to school.
It's the autumnal equinox now. Have you been to the cemetery？
Today is Respect for the Aged Day. Take good care of the elderly.
Today is the autumnal equinox. It's the day when day and night are the same length.
It's a change of clothes. You think it's a shame that you're less exposed or something, don't you？
Have you ever had tsukimi dango？ Rinko hasn't.
Today is Halloween. Trick or treat！ Hiya！
Today is Culture Day, are you being cultural？ ...But what they mean with cultural.
Today is the first day of winter. It's getting colder and colder.
Today is Shichi-Go-San. Rinko wore a furisode when she was a child.
Today is Labor Thanksgiving Day. Hmmm, I don't really know what working is.
Today is the cultural festival. I guess I'm looking forward to it a little bit.
It's almost winter break~. I can't wait.
It's the winter solstice, so I ate pumpkin. I'll also take a yuzu bath.
Today is the Emperor's birthday. In the old days, it was called Tenchousetsu.
Winter break starts today. I want to go snowboarding...
It's Christmas Eve. Of course your plans include Rinko, right？
Today is Eve, huh... No... I didn't expect anything else！
It's Christmas Eve. I wish I could spend it with you all the time.
New Year's Eve already？ Did you have a good year？
Tests, huh. I'm good at humanities subjects.
You finally remembered Rinko. I thought you'd forgotten me.
Good, you remembered. Don't leave Rinko alone again.
What have you been doing all this time？ ...Geez.
I missed you so much. How long are you going to leave me alone... idiot.
I thought I'd never see you again at... Thank goodness.
Again？ Do you really care that much about Rinko？
One hour of gaming a day！ ...I'm kidding. I'm happy to see you.
We meet again. Hehe, is it because you like Rinko？
I don't have enough free time for this, you know？
Ah, there you are. So？ What are you going to do today？
Hehe, you want to play again today？
Maybe in a little while, you know, things will get better, right？
I'm tired of being alone. Let's go play soon.
Nice to see you again. How are you？
I guess it's a bit of a relief to see you.
You came to see me at this hour？ Well, it's good that you're enthusiastic.
What's wrong？ You want to hear Rinko's voice again？
I was just thinking about meeting you now.
There are many things I want to talk about.
Ah, I knew you'd come. Yeah, yeah, just as Rinko predicted.
Oh, here you are... No, I was not thinking about flirting！
Today, you're going to stay with me until Rinko is satisfied.
You are grinning. Well, Rinko's happy too, in her own way.
You need to come see me more often！
Come quickly. I'll show you how much prettier Rinko has become.
It's not fair. It seems like Rinko is the only one who wants to see you.
That's exciting. What are you going to do today？
Are you psyched to see me？ You have to be. Because... so is Rinko.
I've been waiting for you to come see me... I have a lot of things I want to do.
I wish I could come see you from here...
Hehe... I'm so happy. You've come to see me again.
Hehehe... I'm so happy that I laugh.
Rinko hates being alone. Stay with me all the time.
